le=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">References:</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">American Heart Association. (2022). &quot;Physical Activity - How to Get Moving.&quot; </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">Mayo Clinic. (2022). &quot;Exercise: 7 benefits of regular physical activity.&quot; </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">Harvard Health Publishing. (2022). &quot;How to start exercising: A beginner&#39;s guide to working out.&quot; </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\">Centers for Disease Control and Prevention. (2022). &quot;Mobility and aging: Preventing falls and maintaining independence.&quot; </span></p>\r\n', 0, '2024-08-08', '2024-08-08');
