(1, '1698409934.jpg', 'Vijay  Kumar', 'Client', 'A Legacy in the Making!\"\r\nI\'ve never felt more motivated to transform my health than after connecting with this team. They don\'t just focus on immediate changes; they encourage a mindset shift that leads to lasting impact. The support and guidance received here are instrumental in crafting a positive legacy.\r\n\r\n', 1, '2023-10-27 06:02:14', '2024-01-11 01:21:53'),
(2, '1698409946.webp', 'Abhishek  Singh ', 'Client', '\"Inspiring and Impactful!\"\r\nJoining this community has been an eye-opener. Their commitment to turning health struggles into uplifting stories is truly remarkable. They\'ve empowered me to take charge of my physical and mental well-being, allowing me to create a legacy that I\'m proud of.\r\n\r\n', 1, '2023-10-27 06:02:26', '2024-01-11 01:21:48'),
(3, '1702014673.jpg', 'Riddhi  Rawat ', 'Client ', 'Life-Changing Support!\"\r\nTransforming my health journey seemed like an impossible task until I found this incredible team. Their dedication to helping me conquer my health battles not only improved my well-being but also set the stage for a better legacy for my family. I\'m forever grateful for their guidance and support.\r\n\r\n', 1, '2023-10-27 06:02:40', '2024-01-11 01:21:40'),
(4, '1702014723.jpg', 'Rahul Sharma', 'Client ', 'Empowering and Transformative!\"\r\nThe tools and resources provided by this team have been instrumental in my health journey. They\'ve helped me turn struggles into triumphs, creating a legacy of resilience and inspiration for my family and future generations.\r\n\r\n', 1, '2023-12-08 11:22:03', '2024-01-11 01:21:33');
